gr.interamerican.bo2.utils.beans
Class SegmentedDistance<A extends Comparable<? super A>,V>

java.lang.Object
  gr.interamerican.bo2.utils.beans.SegmentedDistance<A,V>
Type Parameters:
A - Type of Range
V - Type of value.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class SegmentedDistance<A extends Comparable<? super A>,V>
extends Object
implements Serializable

SegmentedDistance models a set of segments with a set of Range objects, each linked to a value. The purpose of this class is to find the value that is associated with the range that contains a specified dimension value.
This utility class is suitable for areas with relatively a few segments, because it searches the segments (Ranges) sequentially in order to find which contain the specified dimension value.
